Type of Feat: Class
Specifics: Raise Enemies:</b> For centuries the Dustmen have labored to understand the secrets of death and undeath, and armed with this knowledge the Death Blades are fearsome foes. Three times a day, a Death Blade may animate an opponent as a zombie.

At every even level after 2nd, the zombies raised by the Death Blade become more powerful, gaining an extra two HD, and a +2 bonus to strength.
Use: Selected.